English: These land doctrines were introduced sometimes by directives based on theoretical knowledge and sometimes by a trial and error process. They cover the tactical, organizational and strategic aspects of land combat. There are alternatives  representing different cultural outlooks but also need. A focus on Mobility allows a choice between the blitzkrieg used by the German Wehrmacht and the mass-combat assaults used by the Red Army. A focus on Firepower allows a choice between the offensive fire and movement favoured by the US Army and a more defensive doctrine based upon WWI fighting. The latter provides three different versions of firepower doctrine used by the British, the French and the Japanese.

L?Objectif MobilitÇ part sur une trajectoire orientÇe guerre-Çclair adoptÇe par la Wehrmacht, et sur une trajectoire de combat de masse adoptÇ par l?ArmÇe rouge. L?Objectif Puissance de feu part träs vite sur une trajectoire orientÇe puissance de feu et mouvements, souvent choisie par la US Army, et sur une branche dÇfensive plus gÇnÇrale orientÇe style de combat Grande Guerre. L'importanza sulla potenza di fuoco, a sua volta, si suddivide in una via orientata verso la potenza di fuoco e movimento, preferita dall'esercito e una di carattere pió difensivo, tipica della Prima Guerra Mondiale. English: These air doctrines were introduced sometimes by directives based on theoretical knowledge and sometimes by trial and error process. They all cover the tactical, organizational and strategic aspects of air combat. There are modular branches representing different areas of the air war. The Battlefield Destruction is efficient close air support, Operational Destruction is efficient tactical bombing capability and Strategic Destruction is efficient strategic bombing capability. The first two doctrines also provide Offensive Fighter capability while the latter two give Defensive Fighter capability.

Les deux premiäres zones de modules vous confärent Çgalement des capacitÇs de Chasseur offensif, et les deux derniäres des capacitÇs de Chasseur dÇfensif.
